🇫🇷 The top French health authority has cleared #AstraZeneca's #Covid19 #vaccine for use, but advised against giving it to people over 65 🦠💉

But as @BizotOlivia reports, its efficacy is reported at just 60%, compared with more than 90% for the rival #coronavirus #vaccines.⤵️ https://t.co/tDSaLRhCM0
